ds_my_freeze.description: Issues assigned or lead by user that is marked for freeze

ds_my_latertriage.jql: filter='ds_mystuff' and filter='ds_unresolved' and (project = 'JBIDE' and fixversion in ( %(jbide_bucket_version)s ) or (project = 'JBDS' and fixversion in ( %(jbds_bucket_version)s )))
